6. *Column*: `Column(children: [Text('Hello'), Text('World!')])`
7. *Stack*: `Stack(children: [Text('Hello'), Text('World!')])`
8. *ListView*: `ListView.builder(itemBuilder: (context, index) => Text('Item $index'))`
9. *GridView*: `GridView.builder(gridDelegate: SliverGridDelegateWithFixedCrossAxisCount(crossAxisCount: 2), itemBuilder: (context, index) => Text('Item $index'))`
10. *Image*: `Image.network('(link unavailable)')`
11. *Icon*: `Icon(Icons.star)`
12. *Scaffold*: `Scaffold(appBar: AppBar(title: Text('Hello')), body: Text('World!'))`
13. *AppBar*: `AppBar(title: Text('Hello'))`
14. *Drawer*: `Drawer(child: Text('Hello!'))`
15. *BottomNavigationBar*: `BottomNavigationBar(items: [BottomNavigationBarItem(icon: Icon(Icons.home), label: 'Home')])`
16. *CircularProgressIndicator*: `CircularProgressIndicator()`
17. *LinearProgressIndicator*: `LinearProgressIndicator()`
18. *SnackBar*: `SnackBar(content: Text('Hello!'))`
